    "IOU (GT, P B) = T P T P + F P + F N (15) PB is the Predicted bounding box, GT is the Ground truth bounding box, TP & FP are True Positive and False Positive, and FN is False Negative.",
    "An indicator of object detection accuracy across all classes in a given database is the mean Average Precision (mAP) (Padilla et al. 2020).",
    "Where N is the total number of courses being assessed and AP i is the average precision in the IT class.",
